Class ANNHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.zhaw.it15a_zh.psit3_03.mealmanager.ann.ANNHandler

  • public class ANNHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    Handler for the interaction with an ann.

    Doings: creation of ann, training of ann, validation of ann, calculation of ann, preparation of dataSets and creation of hyperparameter.

      • annHastoBeTrained

        private boolean annHastoBeTrained()
        Checks if an ann has to be trained.
        Returns:
        true if no ann exists, lastTrainingDate of currentAnn is before (now-24hours), trainingsetSize is grown at 10 items (since last training) and if denormalizedError of current Ann is to bad. Else return false.
